import React from 'react'
import { Menu } from 'semantic-ui-react'

class NavBar extends React.Component {
    render() {
        return (
            <Menu>
                <Menu.Item
                    name='editorials'
                  
                    >
                    Editorials
                </Menu.Item>
        
                <Menu.Item
                    name='reviews'
                
                    >
                    Reviews
                </Menu.Item>
        
                <Menu.Item
                    name='upcomingEvents'
                
                    >
                    Upcoming Events
                </Menu.Item>
          </Menu>
        )
    }
}

export default NavBar
